{
  "stem": "20088.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so myself and a few other people walked around, because now we could walk freely in the camp, and we searched and we looked.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was really nothing at all there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we somehow we-- we saw that the barbed-- the electricity wasn't working, so we crawled very-- again, it was-- if it would have been working, we'd have been-- but one of us crawled through the barbed wire to another camp.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we were going to look if there were other people that perhaps feed us and ask if we could do something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we-- it wasn't switched on anymore, the electricity, and we went through several camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was nobody around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we came to one whole camp, which was where the food was stored.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was a [INAUDIBLE] [? cave ?] in food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was everything there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what we were mainly interested was bread, because that we could eat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no-- no cooking facility or anything, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But things which we could eat, just grab like that and eat, we took.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the few of us carried bread back to the people who couldn't walk around, and we gave this to them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then there was the problem of water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everything was frozen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the taps there was no water at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So in the entrance of the camp where the Germans had lived-- because each camp had little barracks where the guards were living-- there was a little pond.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was, of course, frozen, but we found some instrument and we hacked through the ice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we found then as well clothes and blankets and tools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We found everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
